snippet.title: Spider-Man 2 - Nintendo DS Longplay [HD]
snippet.description:
Name: Spider-Man 2

Description: Take New York for a spin. Two years after becoming Spider-Man, you face your toughest enemy yet - the dangerous Doc Ock. Now the city of New York is relying on you to save it from his reckless rampage.

Release Date: November 2004
